HEADWORD: Unpastor
<hw>Un*pas"tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>pastor</ets>.]</ety> <def>To cause to be no longer
